Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.73,0:01:22.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戌时已到
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.63,0:01:24.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉马上要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.27,0:01:26.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了找齐四魂之玉碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.94,0:01:28.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了用这把铁碎牙打败奈落
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.54,0:01:30.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然平常有点好色
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.81,0:01:32.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是其实背负着\N破除风穴诅咒的命运
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.94,0:01:34.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而一直以来都在追杀奈落的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.65,0:01:35.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒法师
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.08,0:01:38.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是感觉到\N和那个人一样的寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.08,0:01:40.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒法师  珊瑚\N七宝跟云母
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.75,0:01:42.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穿梭于时空\N发生在战国时代与现代
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.09,0:01:43.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.02,0:01:44.15,*Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.15,0:01:51.15,OP,,0,0,0,,分散在蓝蓝天空上的 七颗星星
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.05,0:01:55.86,OP,,0,0,0,,每一颗星星 都刻着我的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.17,0:01:59.77,OP,,0,0,0,,就算梦想被粉碎 我也要寻找爱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.07,0:02:03.80,OP,,0,0,0,,我无处可逃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.02,0:02:07.87,OP,,0,0,0,,紧紧抓着我的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.10,0:02:16.30,OP,,0,0,0,,那些骗人的光阴 我再也不会输给它
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.37,0:02:21.67,OP,,0,0,0,,睁大眼睛 看清楚这瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.67,0:02:25.85,OP,,0,0,0,,它仍然紧紧围绕着我们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.12,0:02:29.85,OP,,0,0,0,,让人啜泣的 现实生活中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.85,0:02:33.85,OP,,0,0,0,,最重要的…到底是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.55,0:02:37.72,OP,,0,0,0,,繁忙的这个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.72,0:02:41.95,OP,,0,0,0,,永恒的碎片 忽隐又忽现
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.95,0:02:45.87,OP,,0,0,0,,去触摸 去捕捉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.02,0:02:52.80,OP,,0,0,0,,我们就要循着目标继续向前走
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.97,0:02:58.03,OP,,0,0,0,,为了得到最后的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.03,0:03:05.27,OP,,0,0,0,,我们就要循着目标继续向前走
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.59,0:03:20.59,*Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.45,0:03:49.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.35,0:03:52.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概在大雪中迷路了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.35,0:03:54.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.36,0:04:01.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经没事了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.99,0:04:03.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.93,0:04:06.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的名字叫做小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.57,0:04:10.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你爸爸  他发生什么事了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.97,0:04:12.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我爸爸他…已经死了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.11,0:04:17.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经没有\N可以收容我的地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.31,0:04:19.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你没地方去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.38,0:04:22.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就到我家来住吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.25,0:04:27.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小雪的肌肤
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.65,0:04:29.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像雪一样洁白
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.49,0:04:30.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是个好美丽的姑娘呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.09,0:04:32.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喝!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.49,0:04:36.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…你干嘛突然打我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.90,0:04:39.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是在帮你打蚊子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.40,0:04:41.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,后来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.37,0:04:41.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,后来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.40,0:04:44.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道我之后得修行嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.10,0:04:47.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以就没什么其它特别的事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.61,0:04:49.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你跟那个女的\N后来怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.54,0:04:51.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟她没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.28,0:04:54.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一转眼就过了七年了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.68,0:04:57.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当时我还是个\N乳臭未干的小朋友呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.48,0:05:00.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.02,0:05:05.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看  打中了吧\N哦?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.76,0:05:12.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第101话 七年之后的残雪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.30,0:05:18.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯?那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.07,0:05:21.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你振作点啊  喂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.77,0:05:22.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快睁开眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.44,0:05:24.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可千万不能死啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.88,0:05:25.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要坚强一点哪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.28,0:05:27.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个季节怎么会有雪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.41,0:05:28.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.32,0:05:34.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像醒过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.39,0:05:35.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了  太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.05,0:05:37.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请问一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.06,0:05:39.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出了什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.69,0:05:41.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以的话  能够告诉我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.13,0:05:43.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  是法师啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.06,0:05:47.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近附近\N经常有雪怪出现
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.40,0:05:48.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,村里已经有好几个壮丁
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.83,0:05:50.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像他这样子突然之间…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.84,0:05:53.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你立刻赶去约定会面的小屋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.44,0:05:54.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把这件事告诉他们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.71,0:05:55.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒法师  你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.41,0:05:57.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了阻止妖怪再出来害人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.91,0:05:58.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得先去收拾她
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.21,0:06:00.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  这妖气不是太重
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.08,0:06:01.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会有事的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.85,0:06:06.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这位法师看起来这么年轻
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.35,0:06:08.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会不会出事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.35,0:06:10.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过说起来这个妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.92,0:06:14.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是个\N皮肤雪白的绝色美女呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.03,0:06:19.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,几乎每个男人\N看到她就迷得晕头转向
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.10,0:06:20.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马上跟着她走了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.17,0:06:28.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看样子这里恐怕\N也查不到奈落的线索了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.87,0:06:32.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了  你在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.98,0:06:35.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚刚整理背包时\N从里面翻出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.98,0:06:38.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本来想要带来\N可以跟大家一起玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.25,0:06:40.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果没想到居然给忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.05,0:06:43.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不晓得是不是受潮了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.89,0:06:45.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得先来试试看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.39,0:06:49.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呜哇  这是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.06,0:06:51.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这叫做烟火哦!烟火
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.56,0:06:53.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很漂亮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.57,0:06:55.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唔喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.47,0:06:57.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.20,0:07:00.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么这种时候下雪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.57,0:07:02.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.93,0:07:27.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  弥勒法师…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.50,0:07:28.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒法师
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.17,0:07:30.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒法师
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.51,0:07:39.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这位旅者
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.55,0:07:43.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是不是在大雪中\N遇到麻烦了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.05,0:07:46.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请问有什么我可以帮忙的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.45,0:07:49.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  这位姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.12,0:07:53.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道\N你可不可以帮我生个孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.63,0:07:56.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道你忘啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.46,0:07:59.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,孩子已经生下了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.47,0:08:05.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请去抱抱他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.04,0:08:07.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回去抱抱我们的宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.07,0:08:10.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒法师  你要去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.04,0:08:12.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒法师
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.54,0:08:13.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒法师
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.36,0:08:26.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,云母
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.16,0:08:28.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们两个一起吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.56,0:08:31.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正所谓无功者饭菜不留嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.10,0:08:34.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那几个坏蛋不必留给他们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.00,0:08:35.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.67,0:08:36.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呜哇  看起来真好吃耶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.10,0:08:38.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这个坏蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.00,0:08:41.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是闻到香味才跑回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.87,0:08:42.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别胡说了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.81,0:08:43.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还不是因为突然下雪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.08,0:08:46.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  怪不得觉得这么冷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.11,0:08:48.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚跟弥勒法师呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.01,0:08:50.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  他们还没回来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.58,0:08:51.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过不了多久
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.18,0:08:52.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肚子饿了自然就会回来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.62,0:08:53.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.69,0:08:55.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是我跟云母的鱼耶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.52,0:08:57.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你别说那么小器的话嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.09,0:09:00.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇快过来这边
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.59,0:09:01.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.03,0:09:03.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.10,0:09:09.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  珊瑚  弥勒法师
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.91,0:09:18.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有经过你们的同意\N就自己进来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.41,0:09:19.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.78,0:09:21.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  不要紧啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.41,0:09:22.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且外面的雪下得那么大
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.71,0:09:24.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们来吃点野猪肉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.22,0:09:25.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有很多喔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.05,0:09:27.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇  这真的很好吃耶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.65,0:09:28.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这还是生的耶…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.62,0:09:30.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这叫报应
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.72,0:09:34.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看  在雪女还没离开之前
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.16,0:09:36.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们最好还是先待在这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.36,0:09:38.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雪女?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.73,0:09:39.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.73,0:09:42.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种天气只要有个\N年轻的男人在路上走
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.87,0:09:45.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就会被一个年轻的姑娘叫住
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.80,0:09:47.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迷迷糊糊的跟着姑娘走之后
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.07,0:09:51.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第二天就往往会被人发现\N已经冻死在雪地里了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.64,0:09:56.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说这个小姑娘\N一身肌肤像雪一样白
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.61,0:09:58.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是个样子美若天仙的女人哩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.02,0:10:00.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都说宁可被冻死
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.02,0:10:02.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也要想办法见她一面呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.39,0:10:04.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.62,0:10:07.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这下弥勒法师危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.79,0:10:08.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.39,0:10:10.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚也跟他在一起不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.16,0:10:13.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喔  那大概不要紧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.30,0:10:15.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们真的一点都不了解他
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.03,0:10:19.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看弥勒法师\N绝对不会放过那个姑娘的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.27,0:10:21.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到时候\N要是珊瑚突然出现的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.67,0:10:24.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种情景真不敢想象
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.14,0:10:25.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.04,0:10:27.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这还用问吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.68,0:10:29.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到时候\N珊瑚一定会宰了弥勒法师
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.05,0:10:29.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.68,0:10:32.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同样的话\N以前不知道说过多少次了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.95,0:10:33.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他就是不开窍
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.29,0:10:37.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说的也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.19,0:10:41.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个雪女也是在\N奈落下落不明的时候才现身
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.29,0:10:43.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再怎么说她都是只妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.80,0:10:45.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就绝对不能够放着不管
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.93,0:10:46.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我出去看看马上回来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.43,0:10:48.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉  我跟你一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.20,0:10:49.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.07,0:10:52.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个你们拿去带在身上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.17,0:10:55.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个是回魂汤
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.58,0:10:58.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.48,0:11:00.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.95,0:11:07.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了  云母
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.09,0:11:13.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇啊  大家快来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.46,0:11:17.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.09,0:11:18.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚  喝这个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.96,0:11:19.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个是回魂汤
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.10,0:11:24.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,觉得身体冰冷的时候\N听说喝这个最有效了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.47,0:11:30.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这好像有效哎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.98,0:11:32.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说这是\N酒精浓度特别高的烧酒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.38,0:11:35.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加上蝮蛇  蝾螈\N还有毛毛虫浸泡而成的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.22,0:11:41.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了  她好像恢复精神了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.62,0:11:43.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒怎么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.36,0:11:46.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒法师…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.76,0:11:47.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道你忘啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.53,0:11:50.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,孩子已经生下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.00,0:11:52.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请去抱抱他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.40,0:11:54.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回去抱抱我们的宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.50,0:11:57.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.64,0:12:01.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一家三口\N一定正开心的享受天伦之乐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.87,0:12:02.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.55,0:12:11.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结界
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.15,0:12:20.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来  一起进去吧  相公
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.89,0:12:25.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个女人并不是人类
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.16,0:12:26.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.16,0:12:29.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她为什么要出来到处害人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.40,0:12:31.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像这样抓男人回来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.17,0:12:34.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道就是为了\N要吸收男人身上的精气吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.44,0:12:39.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呜哇
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.78,0:12:40.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.78,0:12:42.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.31,0:12:43.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你终于回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.42,0:12:45.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这…这些是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.92,0:12:49.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相公  就是这些孩子啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.69,0:12:51.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我先进去\N熬点米汤给孩子们喝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.19,0:12:54.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.59,0:12:55.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.33,0:12:57.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呜哇
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.06,0:12:59.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尿布就在那边
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.46,0:13:01.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.70,0:13:05.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.60,0:13:06.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.47,0:13:09.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.08,0:13:13.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你已经忘得一干二净了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.11,0:13:17.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们全都是我帮你生的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.45,0:13:20.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都…都是我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.45,0:13:22.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还这么多?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.86,0:13:27.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我亲耳听见的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.36,0:13:29.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说是法师亲生的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.96,0:13:32.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿  这小子\N也到了该纳税的时候了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.63,0:13:35.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果能这么定下来\N也是件好事不是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.10,0:13:37.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.24,0:13:39.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  你们两个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.74,0:13:42.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妖怪随便说几句\N你们别全当真嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.74,0:13:46.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结界?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.25,0:13:49.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妖气是从里面传出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.75,0:13:52.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.02,0:13:54.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我马上破了这个结界
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.13,0:14:01.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趁现在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.50,0:14:08.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好…乖乖啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.90,0:14:10.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好…乖乖啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.40,0:14:13.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊!别把鼻涕擤在我的衣服上啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.91,0:14:17.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊!我的锡杖不是你们的玩具啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.64,0:14:18.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒法师
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.91,0:14:19.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.01,0:14:21.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帮我喂与作喝点米汤
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.41,0:14:24.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有舍松的尿布湿了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.65,0:14:25.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有待会
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.55,0:14:27.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还要唱歌给小虎听
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.28,0:14:28.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哄他乖乖睡觉哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.15,0:14:29.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  马上去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.66,0:14:32.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  乖乖啦  别再哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.16,0:14:34.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来  好不好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.06,0:14:37.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  马上帮你换尿布哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.66,0:14:39.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小宝宝快睡哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.16,0:14:41.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以在那边尿尿啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.93,0:14:42.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.93,0:14:43.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,厕所在这边嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.54,0:14:49.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.18,0:14:52.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么多小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.41,0:14:54.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是你一个人照顾他们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.55,0:14:57.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身为母亲\N谁不会亲自照顾孩子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.58,0:14:58.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.82,0:15:00.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么多孩子\N难道全都是我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.92,0:15:04.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些孩子的家\N都被战火烧毁了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.92,0:15:09.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每一个一生下来\N就不得不离开他们的母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.33,0:15:12.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我经常捡这些孩子回来照顾
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.96,0:15:14.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久而久之就变成了这么多
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.47,0:15:16.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是…辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.34,0:15:21.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们几个\N全都是可怜的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.95,0:15:30.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心一点哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.85,0:15:31.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在附近
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.99,0:15:37.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这好像是…\N弥勒法师的歌声喔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.96,0:15:38.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么不负责任的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.09,0:15:40.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道他也懂得疼自己的孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.96,0:15:44.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.36,0:15:46.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们看那边
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.23,0:15:49.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有间大屋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.13,0:15:50.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是那里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.10,0:15:54.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,睡得好熟喔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.01,0:15:58.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乖…乖…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.65,0:16:04.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是乖宝宝喔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.62,0:16:06.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要赶快健康长大哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.62,0:16:12.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喔  好乖  好乖
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.52,0:16:14.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好乖  好乖
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.13,0:16:16.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.39,0:16:19.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看样子弥勒法师中了幻术了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.90,0:16:23.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你快醒醒吧  弥勒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.90,0:16:25.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乖…乖…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.77,0:16:26.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.01,0:16:31.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.28,0:16:36.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前面几位来者
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.28,0:16:39.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里不准通行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.56,0:16:47.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦  是四魂之玉碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.06,0:16:50.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出来吧  雪豹
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.67,0:17:01.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要勉强啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.71,0:17:03.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天气这么冷\N四肢当然不容易伸展
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.18,0:17:06.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我打倒他们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.58,0:17:08.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后把四魂之玉碎片抢过来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.18,0:17:13.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死妖怪  今天让我来收拾你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.82,0:17:19.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼  搞定了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.59,0:17:22.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到这家伙这么不堪一击
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.69,0:17:23.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃啊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.36,0:17:24.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.96,0:17:25.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.46,0:17:27.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呀啊  什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.24,0:17:32.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉  快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.12,0:17:47.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乖乖哦  乖乖哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.62,0:17:49.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请问一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.72,0:17:52.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,外面好像有点吵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.76,0:17:53.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是出了什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.49,0:17:56.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一群野狗在雪地迷了路了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.36,0:17:59.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你什么都不必担心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.73,0:18:02.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我马上派人把它们赶走
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.37,0:18:03.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看招
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.01,0:18:09.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宝宝们…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.88,0:18:14.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.78,0:18:16.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.01,0:18:17.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你快醒醒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.52,0:18:19.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我本来就很清醒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.75,0:18:21.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你自己仔细看看  这也叫清醒喔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.65,0:18:25.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…这些是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.23,0:18:31.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天休想逃离这里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.06,0:18:33.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你长得和那个人那么像
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.60,0:18:35.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和我所认识的那个人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.00,0:18:39.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以其实我也不想\N对你这么的粗鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.24,0:18:48.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咿呀  怎么这么不顺利啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.51,0:18:51.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飞来骨
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.72,0:18:54.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好快哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.35,0:18:54.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.85,0:18:58.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风之伤
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.53,0:19:08.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然让它闪开了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.83,0:19:10.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恨…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.84,0:19:12.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太可恨了…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.47,0:19:14.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你明明心地那么的善良
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.37,0:19:16.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么偏偏要诱捕那些男人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.11,0:19:18.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并且加害他们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.51,0:19:20.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恨…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.11,0:19:22.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个世界太可恨了…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.72,0:19:28.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我恨我自己活在这个世上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.39,0:19:30.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我恨啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.39,0:19:36.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放下屠刀才能够立地成佛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.56,0:19:40.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得罪了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.41,0:19:50.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.28,0:19:55.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙\N怎么突然变成这样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.18,0:19:56.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要用热
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.01,0:19:58.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们最怕热气跟火了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.05,0:20:00.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧  那就看我的狐火
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.79,0:20:03.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看招
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.96,0:20:12.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一点都不管用嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.16,0:20:14.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  对了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.20,0:20:16.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以利用这个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.17,0:20:17.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这边
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.90,0:20:19.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我陪你过两招吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.94,0:20:21.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.81,0:20:30.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飞来骨
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.36,0:20:45.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是现在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.70,0:20:47.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风之伤
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.48,0:21:08.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那也是另一只雪怪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.25,0:21:10.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  让我来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.65,0:21:11.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.39,0:21:13.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我相信刚刚那个雪怪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.73,0:21:16.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经没有附身在这个灵魂上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.48,0:21:40.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个灵魂\N属于一个被卷入战争
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.52,0:21:43.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并且丢了性命的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.26,0:21:46.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以\N她一直在寻找那些
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.16,0:21:51.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因不幸而离开人世的\N那些小孩的灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.53,0:21:52.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚至一直照顾着他们
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.13,0:21:55.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我相信这个女人的灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.13,0:21:57.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是被雪怪给控制住了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.10,0:21:59.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是哀伤
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.50,0:22:02.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想战国时代的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.64,0:22:04.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该活得很艰辛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.71,0:22:05.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话又说回来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.94,0:22:07.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一开始当她告诉你\N替你生了孩子的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.21,0:22:09.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么想都不想就相信了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.71,0:22:12.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是有\N做过什么见不得人的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.65,0:22:14.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.02,0:22:16.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是个傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.95,0:22:17.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.89,0:22:22.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒法师\N是为了帮助可怜的妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.33,0:22:23.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才会故意假装中计吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.33,0:22:24.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.83,0:22:27.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错  就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.73,0:22:32.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身为法师\N怎么可能会犯下这种错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.40,0:22:33.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.71,0:22:37.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又是一只蚊子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.71,0:22:39.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.04,0:22:42.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多该继续上路了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.55,0:22:43.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.55,0:22:48.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟那位姑娘真的好像喔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.45,0:22:49.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.22,0:22:50.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.06,0:22:55.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那天帮助\N年纪还小的我的那个人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.16,0:22:59.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那位小雪姑娘…一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.10,0:23:02.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正在世界的某个角落
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.83,0:23:04.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过着幸福快乐的日子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.68,0:23:19.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是残雪…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.65,0:24:56.65,ED,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.50,0:23:34.15,ED,,0,0,0,,红红的太阳照亮一切
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.72,0:23:43.95,ED,,0,0,0,,也照遍过去和现在
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.10,0:23:53.22,ED,,0,0,0,,那些夕阳下的想象
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.52,0:24:03.22,ED,,0,0,0,,这颗心真的能承担吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.75,0:24:08.20,ED,,0,0,0,,告诉我什么办法才能
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.50,0:24:13.12,ED,,0,0,0,,活得比以前更开朗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.12,0:24:20.52,ED,,0,0,0,,这么做就算会让自己委屈
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.40,0:24:27.07,ED,,0,0,0,,要默默承受伤害
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.07,0:24:31.25,ED,,0,0,0,,会失去一切
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.65,0:24:38.50,ED,,0,0,0,,真正的歌仍会不断在我心中回荡
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.95,0:24:48.52,ED,,0,0,0,,真正的歌才是我的路标
